1 I will exalt you, O my God and my King, and will bless your name for ever.
2 Every day I will bless you, and I will praise your name for ever.
3 Great is God! He deserves our praise, and his greatness has no end.
4 One generation shall laud your works, to another declare your power.
5 On the glorious splendour of your majesty I will meditate.
6 The Lord is just in all his ways, and loving in all his works.
